{"id":1373,"date":"2019-01-10T16:36:17","date_gmt":"2019-01-10T09:36:17","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/thietkethicongdn.com\/?p=1373"},"modified":"2019-01-11T16:52:48","modified_gmt":"2019-01-11T09:52:48","slug":"bat-mi-thiet-ke-sanh-khach-san-dep-lung-linh-va-an-tuong-nhat-2019","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"https:\/\/thietkethicongdn.com\/bat-mi-thiet-ke-sanh-khach-san-dep-lung-linh-va-an-tuong-nhat-2019","title":{"rendered":"[B\u1eacT M\u00cd] Thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf s\u1ea3nh kh\u00e1ch s\u1ea1n \u0111\u1eb9p lung linh v\u00e0 \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng nh\u1ea5t 2019"},"content":{"rendered":"<div class=\"news-container\">\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf s\u1ea3nh kh\u00e1ch s\u1ea1n mini l\u00e0 s\u1ef1 k\u1ebft h\u1ee3p h\u00e0i h\u00f2a gi\u1eefa ki\u1ebfn tr\u00fac v\u00e0 n\u1ed9i th\u1ea5t gi\u00fap kh\u00f4ng gian tr\u1edf n\u00ean r\u1ed9ng r\u00e3i sang tr\u1ecdng v\u00e0 \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng h\u01a1n. S\u1ea3nh kh\u00e1ch s\u1ea1n ch\u00ednh l\u00e0 \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean khi du kh\u00e1ch b\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00e0o kh\u00e1ch s\u1ea1n. Do \u0111\u00f3 h\u00f4m nay, <strong>Thietkethicongdn.com<\/strong> xin gi\u1edbi thi\u1ec7u t\u1edbi qu\u00fd b\u1ea1n \u0111\u1ecdc nh\u1eefng\u00a0<span style=\"color: #0000ff;\"><a style=\"color: #0000ff;\" href=\"https:\/\/thietkethicongdn.com\/bat-mi-thiet-ke-sanh-khach-san-dep-lung-linh-va-an-tuong-nhat-2019\"><em><strong>[B\u1eacT M\u00cd] Thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf s\u1ea3nh kh\u00e1ch s\u1ea1n \u0111\u1eb9p lung linh\u00a0\u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng nh\u1ea5t 2019<\/strong><\/em><\/a><\/span>. H\u00e3y c\u00f9ng theo d\u00f5i nh\u00e9!<\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"size-full wp-image-1387 aligncenter\" src=\"https:\/\/thietkethicongdn.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/01\/B\u1eacT-M\u00cd-Thi\u1ebft-k\u1ebf-s\u1ea3nh-kh\u00e1ch-s\u1ea1n-\u0111\u1eb9p-lung-linh-v\u00e0-\u1ea5n-t\u01b0\u1ee3ng-nh\u1ea5t-201913.jpeg\" alt=\"\" width=\"700\" height=\"489\" \/><\/p>\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>[B\u1eacT M\u00cd] Thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf s\u1ea3nh kh\u00e1ch s\u1ea1n \u0111\u1eb9p lung linh v\u00e0 \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng nh\u1ea5t 2019<\/strong><\/h2>\n<h3 style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>1. S\u1ea3nh kh\u00e1ch s\u1ea1n l\u00e0 g\u00ec?<\/strong><\/h3>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&#8211; S\u1ea3nh kh\u00e1ch s\u1ea1n th\u01b0\u1eddng l\u00e0 khu v\u1ef1c \u0111\u1eb9p nh\u1ea5t v\u00e0 trang tr\u1ecdng nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a kh\u00e1ch s\u1ea1n. B\u01b0\u1edbc ch\u00e2n v\u00e0o kh\u00e1ch s\u1ea1n, d\u00f9 l\u00e0 kh\u00e1ch s\u1ea1n mini, chu\u1ed7i kh\u00e1ch s\u1ea1n hay Resort ngh\u0129 d\u01b0\u1ee1ng, nh\u1eefng ng\u01b0\u1eddi m\u00e0 du kh\u00e1ch ti\u1ebfp x\u00fac \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean s\u1ebd l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng ng\u01b0\u1eddi l\u00e0m vi\u1ec7c \u1edf ti\u1ec1n s\u1ea3nh.<\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&#8211; <strong>S\u1ea3nh kh\u00e1ch s\u1ea1n<\/strong>\u00a0\u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c v\u00ed nh\u01b0 &#8220;trung t\u00e2m th\u1ea7n kinh&#8221; c\u1ee7a kh\u00e1ch s\u1ea1n, s\u1ea3nh kh\u00e1ch s\u1ea1n\u00a0bao g\u1ed3m: B\u1ed9 ph\u1eadn s\u1ea3nh l\u1ec5 t\u00e2n c\u00f3 ch\u1ee9c n\u0103ng nh\u01b0 chi\u1ebfc c\u1ea7u n\u1ed1i gi\u1eefa kh\u00e1ch h\u00e0ng v\u00e0 c\u00e1c b\u1ed9 ph\u1eadn c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i trong kh\u00e1ch s\u1ea1n \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u00e1p \u1ee9ng v\u00e0 th\u1ecfa m\u00e3n nhu c\u1ea7u ch\u00ednh \u0111\u00e1ng.<\/p>\n<figure id=\"attachment_1374\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-1374\" style=\"width: 700px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"wp-image-1374 size-full\" src=\"https:\/\/thietkethicongdn.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/01\/B\u1eacT-M\u00cd-Thi\u1ebft-k\u1ebf-s\u1ea3nh-kh\u00e1ch-s\u1ea1n-\u0111\u1eb9p-lung-linh-v\u00e0-\u1ea5n-t\u01b0\u1ee3ng-nh\u1ea5t-2019.jpeg\" alt=\"\" width=\"700\" height=\"466\" \/><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-1374\" class=\"wp-caption-text\"><em>(Thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf s\u1ea3nh kh\u00e1ch s\u1ea1n sang tr\u1ecdng l\u00e0 n\u01a1i &#8220;trung t\u00e2m th\u1ea7n kinh&#8221; c\u1ee7a kh\u00e1ch s\u1ea1n)<\/em><\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<blockquote><p><em>&gt;&gt;&gt; XEM TH\u00caM\u00a0<span style=\"color: #0000ff;\"><a style=\"color: #0000ff;\" href=\"https:\/\/thietkethicongdn.com\/ban-ve-thiet-ke-nha-hang-tiec-cuoi-tong-quan-tieu-chuan-ban-ve\"><strong>B\u1ea3n v\u1ebd thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf nh\u00e0 h\u00e0ng ti\u1ec7c c\u01b0\u1edbi \u2013 T\u1ed5ng quan, ti\u00eau chu\u1ea9n, b\u1ea3n v\u1ebd<\/strong><\/a><\/span><\/em><\/p><\/blockquote>\n<h3 style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>2. S\u1ea3nh kh\u00e1ch s\u1ea1n bao g\u1ed3m nh\u1eefng v\u1ecb tr\u00ed n\u00e0o?<\/strong><\/h3>\n<ul style=\"text-align: justify;\">\n<li>Nh\u00e2n vi\u00ean ti\u1ebfp t\u00e2n\u00a0(Receptionist)<\/li>\n<li>Nh\u00e2n vi\u00ean \u0111\u1eb7t ph\u00f2ng (Reservationist)<\/li>\n<li>Nh\u00e2n vi\u00ean g\u00e1c c\u1eeda (Uniformed Staff)<\/li>\n<li>Nh\u00e2n vi\u00ean giao t\u1ebf (Guest Relation Officer)<\/li>\n<li>Nh\u00e2n vi\u00ean t\u1ed5ng \u0111\u00e0i (Telephone Operator)<\/li>\n<li>Nh\u00e2n vi\u00ean k\u1ebf to\u00e1n (Cashier\/Night Auditors)<\/li>\n<li>Nh\u00e2n vi\u00ean h\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 kh\u00e1ch h\u00e0ng (Concierge)<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<h3 style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>3. C\u00e1c m\u1eabu thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf s\u1ea3nh kh\u00e1ch s\u1ea1n \u0111\u1eb9p m\u00ea h\u1ed3n<\/strong><\/h3>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tr\u00ean th\u1ef1c t\u1ebf, s\u1ea3nh kh\u00e1ch s\u1ea1n l\u00e0 s\u1ef1 pha tr\u1ed9n c\u1ee7a h\u00ecnh th\u1ee9c v\u00e0 c\u00f4ng n\u0103ng, th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n nhu c\u1ea7u c\u1ee7a kh\u00e1ch h\u00e0ng v\u00e0 bi\u1ec3u hi\u1ec7n phong c\u00e1ch m\u00e0 kh\u00e1ch s\u1ea1n mu\u1ed1n h\u01b0\u1edbng t\u1edbi.<\/p>\n<figure id=\"attachment_1375\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-1375\" style=\"width: 700px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"wp-image-1375 size-full\" src=\"https:\/\/thietkethicongdn.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/01\/B\u1eacT-M\u00cd-Thi\u1ebft-k\u1ebf-s\u1ea3nh-kh\u00e1ch-s\u1ea1n-\u0111\u1eb9p-lung-linh-v\u00e0-\u1ea5n-t\u01b0\u1ee3ng-nh\u1ea5t-20191.jpeg\" alt=\"\" width=\"700\" height=\"430\" \/><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-1375\" class=\"wp-caption-text\"><em>(B\u01b0\u1edbc ch\u00e2n v\u00e0o s\u1ea3nh kh\u00e1ch s\u1ea1n th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n s\u1ef1 trang tr\u1ecdng t\u1ea1o d\u1ea5u \u1ea5n s\u00e2u s\u1eafc cho kh\u00e1ch h\u00e0ng)<\/em><\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<h4 style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>3.1. Thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf s\u1ea3nh kh\u00e1ch s\u1ea1n hi\u1ec7n \u0111\u1ea1i<\/strong><\/h4>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&#8211; Thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf s\u1ea3nh kh\u00e1ch s\u1ea1n hi\u1ec7n \u0111\u1ea1i, ti\u1ec7n nghi \u0111\u1ec3 t\u1ea1o n\u00ean m\u1ed9t \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng s\u00e2u s\u1eafc ngay t\u1eeb c\u00e1i nh\u00ecn \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean cho kh\u00e1ch h\u00e0ng v\u1edbi c\u00e1c m\u1eabu thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf s\u1ea3nh kh\u00e1ch s\u1ea1n ph\u00f9 h\u1ee3p tu\u00e2n th\u1ee7 theo ti\u00eau chu\u1ea9n thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf kh\u00e1ch s\u1ea1n.<\/p>\n<blockquote><p><em>&gt;&gt;&gt; THAM KH\u1ea2O NGAY\u00a0<span style=\"color: #0000ff;\"><strong><a style=\"color: #0000ff;\" href=\"https:\/\/thietkethicongdn.com\/tieu-chuan-thiet-ke-khach-san-3-sao-4-sao-5-sao-6-sao-moi-nhat-2019\">Ti\u00eau chu\u1ea9n thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf kh\u00e1ch s\u1ea1n 3 sao, 4 sao, 5 sao, 6 sao m\u1edbi nh\u1ea5t 2019<\/a><\/strong><\/span><\/em><\/p><\/blockquote>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"size-full wp-image-1378 aligncenter\" src=\"https:\/\/thietkethicongdn.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/01\/B\u1eacT-M\u00cd-Thi\u1ebft-k\u1ebf-s\u1ea3nh-kh\u00e1ch-s\u1ea1n-\u0111\u1eb9p-lung-linh-v\u00e0-\u1ea5n-t\u01b0\u1ee3ng-nh\u1ea5t-20194.jpeg\" alt=\"\" width=\"700\" height=\"436\" \/><\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"size-medium wp-image-1379 aligncenter\" src=\"https:\/\/thietkethicongdn.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/01\/B\u1eacT-M\u00cd-Thi\u1ebft-k\u1ebf-s\u1ea3nh-kh\u00e1ch-s\u1ea1n-\u0111\u1eb9p-lung-linh-v\u00e0-\u1ea5n-t\u01b0\u1ee3ng-nh\u1ea5t-20195.jpeg\" alt=\"\" width=\"700\" height=\"379\" \/><\/p>\n<h4 style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>3.2. Thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf s\u1ea3nh kh\u00e1ch s\u1ea1n t\u00e2n c\u1ed5 \u0111i\u1ec3n<\/strong><\/h4>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&#8211; Theo c\u00e1c ki\u1ebfn tr\u00fac s\u01b0 chuy\u00ean thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf kh\u00e1ch s\u1ea1n th\u00ec:\u00a0<strong>thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf n\u1ed9i th\u1ea5t s\u1ea3nh kh\u00e1ch s\u1ea1n<\/strong>\u00a0\u0111\u00fang ti\u00eau chu\u1ea9n,\u00a0h\u00fat m\u1eaft l\u00e0 y\u1ebfu t\u1ed1 quan tr\u1ecdng gi\u00fap n\u00edu ch\u00e2n m\u1ecdi kh\u00e1ch h\u00e0ng mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u1ebfn v\u1edbi kh\u00e1ch s\u1ea1n. Do \u0111\u00f3, vi\u1ec7c trang tr\u00ed n\u1ed9i th\u1ea5t ph\u00f9 h\u1ee3p\u00a0t\u1ea1o n\u00ean\u00a0kh\u00f4ng gian th\u00e2n thi\u1ec7n, \u1ea5m \u00e1p v\u00e0 sang tr\u1ecdng.<\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&#8211; \u0110i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n t\u1eeb\u00a0m\u00e0u s\u1eafc thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf, th\u1ea3m tr\u1ea3i, b\u00e0i tr\u00ed \u0111\u1ed3 g\u1ed7 n\u1ed9i th\u1ea5t&#8230; V\u1eady n\u00ean, b\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00e0o\u00a0s\u1ea3nh c\u1ee7a m\u1ed9t kh\u00e1ch s\u1ea1n c\u0169ng gi\u1ed1ng nh\u01b0 vi\u1ec7c b\u1eaft tay m\u1ed9t ng\u01b0\u1eddi n\u00e0o \u0111\u00f3 m\u00e0 b\u1ea1n v\u1eeba g\u1eb7p. \u0110\u00f3 \u0111\u1ec1u l\u00e0 \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean m\u00e0 du kh\u00e1ch quan t\u00e2m khi \u0111\u1ebfn v\u1edbi kh\u00e1ch s\u1ea1n c\u1ee7a b\u1ea1n.<\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"size-full wp-image-1380 aligncenter\" src=\"https:\/\/thietkethicongdn.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/01\/B\u1eacT-M\u00cd-Thi\u1ebft-k\u1ebf-s\u1ea3nh-kh\u00e1ch-s\u1ea1n-\u0111\u1eb9p-lung-linh-v\u00e0-\u1ea5n-t\u01b0\u1ee3ng-nh\u1ea5t-20196.jpeg\" alt=\"\" width=\"700\" height=\"579\" \/><\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"size-medium wp-image-1381 aligncenter\" src=\"https:\/\/thietkethicongdn.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/01\/B\u1eacT-M\u00cd-Thi\u1ebft-k\u1ebf-s\u1ea3nh-kh\u00e1ch-s\u1ea1n-\u0111\u1eb9p-lung-linh-v\u00e0-\u1ea5n-t\u01b0\u1ee3ng-nh\u1ea5t-20197.jpeg\" alt=\"\" width=\"700\" height=\"466\" \/><\/p>\n<h4 style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>3.3. Thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf s\u1ea3nh kh\u00e1ch s\u1ea1n mini<\/strong><\/h4>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&#8211; <strong>C\u00f3 th\u1ec3 th\u1ea5y:<\/strong> Nh\u1eefng s\u1ea3nh kh\u00e1ch s\u1ea1n t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t t\u1ea1o n\u00ean m\u1ed9t n\u01a1i an to\u00e0n \u0111\u1ec3 d\u1eebng ch\u00e2n cho kh\u00e1ch du l\u1ecbch, cho nh\u1eefng th\u01b0\u01a1ng gia, nh\u1eefng ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111i c\u00f4ng t\u00e1c, nh\u1eefng c\u1eb7p t\u00ecnh nh\u00e2n \u0111i ngh\u1ec9 cu\u1ed1i tu\u1ea7n \u1edf xa.<\/p>\n<figure id=\"attachment_1382\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-1382\" style=\"width: 700px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"wp-image-1382 size-full\" src=\"https:\/\/thietkethicongdn.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/01\/B\u1eacT-M\u00cd-Thi\u1ebft-k\u1ebf-s\u1ea3nh-kh\u00e1ch-s\u1ea1n-\u0111\u1eb9p-lung-linh-v\u00e0-\u1ea5n-t\u01b0\u1ee3ng-nh\u1ea5t-20198.jpeg\" alt=\"\" width=\"700\" height=\"318\" \/><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-1382\" class=\"wp-caption-text\"><em>(<strong>Thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf s\u1ea3nh kh\u00e1ch s\u1ea1n mini<\/strong> tho\u00e1ng \u0111\u00e3ng v\u00e0 mang phong c\u00e1ch m\u1edbi l\u1ea1)<\/em><\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<h4 style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>3.4. Thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf s\u1ea3nh kh\u00e1ch s\u1ea1n 3 sao\u00a0<\/strong><\/h4>\n<figure id=\"attachment_1383\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-1383\" style=\"width: 700px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"wp-image-1383 size-full\" src=\"https:\/\/thietkethicongdn.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/01\/B\u1eacT-M\u00cd-Thi\u1ebft-k\u1ebf-s\u1ea3nh-kh\u00e1ch-s\u1ea1n-\u0111\u1eb9p-lung-linh-v\u00e0-\u1ea5n-t\u01b0\u1ee3ng-nh\u1ea5t-20199.jpeg\" alt=\"\" width=\"700\" height=\"430\" \/><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-1383\" class=\"wp-caption-text\"><em>(\u1ede thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf s\u1ea3nh kh\u00e1ch s\u1ea1n 3 sao hi\u1ec7n \u0111\u1ea1i, kh\u00f4ng gian m\u1edf v\u1edbi k\u00ednh c\u01b0\u1eddng l\u1ef1c l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u kh\u00f3 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 b\u1ecf qua)<\/em><\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<figure id=\"attachment_1384\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-1384\" style=\"width: 700px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"wp-image-1384 size-full\" src=\"https:\/\/thietkethicongdn.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/01\/B\u1eacT-M\u00cd-Thi\u1ebft-k\u1ebf-s\u1ea3nh-kh\u00e1ch-s\u1ea1n-\u0111\u1eb9p-lung-linh-v\u00e0-\u1ea5n-t\u01b0\u1ee3ng-nh\u1ea5t-201910.jpeg\" alt=\"\" width=\"700\" height=\"466\" \/><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-1384\" class=\"wp-caption-text\"><em>(Thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf s\u1ea3nh kh\u00e1ch s\u1ea1n 3 sao phong c\u00e1ch t\u00e2n c\u1ed5 \u0111i\u1ec3n, mang h\u01a1i h\u01b0\u1edbng Ch\u00e2u \u00c2u qu\u00fd t\u1ed9c)<\/em><\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<h4 style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>3.5. Thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf s\u1ea3nh kh\u00e1ch s\u1ea1n 5 sao<\/strong><\/h4>\n<figure id=\"attachment_1385\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-1385\" style=\"width: 700px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"wp-image-1385 size-full\" src=\"https:\/\/thietkethicongdn.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/01\/B\u1eacT-M\u00cd-Thi\u1ebft-k\u1ebf-s\u1ea3nh-kh\u00e1ch-s\u1ea1n-\u0111\u1eb9p-lung-linh-v\u00e0-\u1ea5n-t\u01b0\u1ee3ng-nh\u1ea5t-201911.jpeg\" alt=\"\" width=\"700\" height=\"280\" \/><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-1385\" class=\"wp-caption-text\"><em>(M\u1ed9t thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf s\u1ea3nh kh\u00e1ch s\u1ea1n 5 sao tr\u00e1ng l\u1ec7, th\u01b0\u1ee3ng h\u1ea1ng)<\/em><\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<h3 style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>4. Nguy\u00ean t\u1eafc, nguy\u00ean l\u00fd thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf s\u1ea3nh kh\u00e1ch s\u1ea1n \u0111\u1eb9p<\/strong><\/h3>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Trong thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf ki\u1ebfn tr\u00fac, c\u0169ng gi\u1ed1ng nh\u01b0 con ng\u01b0\u1eddi, \u0111\u1ea1i s\u1ea3nh kh\u00e1ch s\u1ea1n l\u00e0 hi\u1ec7n th\u00e2n c\u1ee7a t\u00ednh c\u00e1ch. M\u1ed9t s\u1ea3nh kh\u00e1ch s\u1ea1n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 c\u00f3 d\u00e1ng v\u1ebb kh\u00e1ch kh\u00ed, m\u1ebfm kh\u00e1ch, ho\u1eb7c th\u00e2n thi\u1ec7n. L\u00e0 ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e2n c\u1ee7a kh\u00e1ch s\u1ea1n, c\u00e1c b\u1ea1n kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ee9ng b\u00ean c\u1eeda tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u1ec3 ch\u00e0o \u0111\u00f3n t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 c\u00e1c kh\u00e1ch b\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00e0o kh\u00e1ch s\u1ea1n c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c b\u1ea1n, nh\u01b0ng c\u00e1c b\u1ea1n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf \u0111\u1ea1i s\u1ea3nh kh\u00e1ch s\u1ea1n c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh th\u00e0nh m\u1ed9t \u1ed1c \u0111\u1ea3o \u0111\u1ea7y thu h\u00fat v\u00e0 ph\u00f9 h\u1ee3p v\u1edbi <strong>xu h\u01b0\u1edbng thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf ki\u1ebfn tr\u00fac kh\u00e1ch s\u1ea1n<\/strong> hi\u1ec7n nay.<\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"size-full wp-image-1377 aligncenter\" src=\"https:\/\/thietkethicongdn.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/01\/B\u1eacT-M\u00cd-Thi\u1ebft-k\u1ebf-s\u1ea3nh-kh\u00e1ch-s\u1ea1n-\u0111\u1eb9p-lung-linh-v\u00e0-\u1ea5n-t\u01b0\u1ee3ng-nh\u1ea5t-20193.jpeg\" alt=\"\" width=\"700\" height=\"477\" \/><\/p>\n<ul style=\"text-align: justify;\">\n<li>Thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf s\u1ea3nh kh\u00e1ch s\u1ea1n, thang m\u00e1y v\u00e0 l\u1ed1i tho\u00e1t hi\u1ec3m \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf r\u1ed9ng r\u00e3i, th\u00f4ng tho\u00e1ng, t\u1ea1o \u0111i\u1ec1u ki\u1ec7n thu\u1eadn l\u1ee3i cho s\u1ef1 di chuy\u1ec3n c\u1ee7a kh\u00e1ch h\u00e0ng.<\/li>\n<li>Qu\u1ea7y l\u00ea t\u00e2n, khu v\u1ef1c ch\u1edd, thang m\u00e1y \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c b\u1ed1 tr\u00ed c\u00e1c h\u1ec7 th\u1ed1ng \u0111\u00e8n ch\u00f9m v\u00e0 \u0111\u00e8n \u00e2m tr\u1ea7n chi\u1ebfu s\u00e1ng lung linh, mang \u0111\u1ebfn kh\u00f4ng gian sang tr\u1ecdng, qu\u00fd ph\u00e1i.<\/li>\n<li>Th\u01b0\u01a1ng hi\u1ec7u, logo c\u1ee7a kh\u00e1ch s\u1ea1n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf g\u1ea7n b\u00e0n l\u1ec5 t\u00e2n th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1ef1 chuy\u00ean nghi\u1ec7p, t\u1ea1o n\u00ean \u0111i\u1ec3m nh\u1ea5n cho s\u1ea3nh v\u00e0 kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh v\u1ecb th\u1ebf c\u1ee7a kh\u00e1ch s\u1ea1n.<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"size-full wp-image-1386 aligncenter\" src=\"https:\/\/thietkethicongdn.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/01\/B\u1eacT-M\u00cd-Thi\u1ebft-k\u1ebf-s\u1ea3nh-kh\u00e1ch-s\u1ea1n-\u0111\u1eb9p-lung-linh-v\u00e0-\u1ea5n-t\u01b0\u1ee3ng-nh\u1ea5t-201912.jpeg\" alt=\"\" width=\"700\" height=\"466\" \/><\/p>\n<\/div>\n<div class=\"news-container\">\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ngo\u00e0i thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf n\u1ed9i th\u1ea5t s\u1ea3nh kh\u00e1ch s\u1ea1n, ch\u00fang t\u00f4i c\u00f2n<strong>\u00a0thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf n\u1ed9i th\u1ea5t kh\u00e1ch s\u1ea1n<\/strong>\u00a0theo c\u00e1c h\u1ea1ng m\u1ee5c kh\u00e1c. N\u1ebfu c\u00e1c b\u1ea1n c\u00f3 nhu c\u1ea7u t\u01b0 v\u1ea5n\u00a0<strong>thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf kh\u00e1ch s\u1ea1n<\/strong>\u00a0c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 li\u00ean h\u1ec7 tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp v\u1edbi ch\u00fang t\u00f4i theo Hotline:\u00a0<strong><a href=\"tel:0932544404\">088 664 44 04<\/a>\u00a0<\/strong>\u0111\u1ec3 bi\u1ebft th\u00eam th\u00f4ng tin chi ti\u1ebft.<\/p>\n<\/div>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>Thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf s\u1ea3nh kh\u00e1ch s\u1ea1n mini l\u00e0 s\u1ef1 k\u1ebft h\u1ee3p h\u00e0i h\u00f2a gi\u1eefa ki\u1ebfn tr\u00fac v\u00e0 n\u1ed9i th\u1ea5t gi\u00fap kh\u00f4ng gian tr\u1edf n\u00ean r\u1ed9ng r\u00e3i sang tr\u1ecdng v\u00e0 \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng h\u01a1n. S\u1ea3nh kh\u00e1ch s\u1ea1n ch\u00ednh l\u00e0 \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean khi du kh\u00e1ch b\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00e0o kh\u00e1ch s\u1ea1n. Do \u0111\u00f3 h\u00f4m nay, Thietkethicongdn.com xin gi\u1edbi thi\u1ec7u&#8230;<\/p>\n","protected":false},"author":3,"featured_media":1387,"comment_status":"open","ping_status":"open","sticky":false,"template":"","format":"standard","meta":{"footnotes":""},"categories":[5],"tags":[],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/thietkethicongdn.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/1373"}],"collection":[{"href":"https:\/\/thietkethicongdn.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts"}],"about":[{"href":"https:\/\/thietkethicongdn.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/types\/post"}],"author":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/thietkethicongdn.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/users\/3"}],"replies":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/thietkethicongdn.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/comments?post=1373"}],"version-history":[{"count":5,"href":"https:\/\/thietkethicongdn.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/1373\/revisions"}],"predecessor-version":[{"id":1410,"href":"https:\/\/thietkethicongdn.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/1373\/revisions\/1410"}],"wp:featuredmedia":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/thietkethicongdn.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media\/1387"}],"wp:attachment":[{"href":"https:\/\/thietkethicongdn.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media?parent=1373"}],"wp:term":[{"taxonomy":"category","embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/thietkethicongdn.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/categories?post=1373"},{"taxonomy":"post_tag","embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/thietkethicongdn.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/tags?post=1373"}],"curies":[{"name":"wp","href":"https:\/\/api.w.org\/{